### Health check
GET http://localhost:5141/health

### Create escrow (requires JWT token)
POST http://localhost:5141/api/escrows
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "listingId": "67890abcdef1234567890abc",
  "sellerId": "12345abcdef1234567890abc",
  "amount": 5000000
}

### Get escrow by ID
GET http://localhost:5141/api/escrows/67890abcdef1234567890abc
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get escrow by order ID
GET http://localhost:5141/api/escrows/order/67890abcdef1234567890abc
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get buyer's escrows
GET http://localhost:5141/api/escrows/buyer
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get seller's escrows
GET http://localhost:5141/api/escrows/seller
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Release escrow to seller
POST http://localhost:5141/api/escrows/67890abcdef1234567890abc/release
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Buyer confirmed delivery"
}

### Refund escrow to buyer
POST http://localhost:5141/api/escrows/67890abcdef1234567890abc/refund
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Product not as described"
}

### Payment webhook
POST http://localhost:5141/api/webhooks/payment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "evt_test_123",
  "event_type": "payment.captured",
  "payment_intent_id": "pi_test_456",
  "amount": 5000000,
  "currency": "VND",
  "status": "succeeded"
}

